item.title: Austinscape V3.1
item.dc:creator: @hippie408 hippie408
item.description:
@hippie408 wrote:

I agree this is terrible lol…About 6 months old now. Might release V4…Final version probably.

Everywhere is not wilderness, except the wilderness itself. My skull interface at the bottom is messed up, not hard to change. As for tabs, those were ‘In’ at the time. I now have Tabs and ancient teleports (At that time, like, no one had reg teles). Plus new mini games in the current one with some more updates. Better members stuff, only one portal, about 4 new minis. Lets see… V4 will have COMPLETE anti-SYI, thanks to Gnarly on Run3 l0cus. This one has working pets that follow you, not just cats…Member’s only, too. Pets are like, ghosts, gorillas, obby guys, and like , 5 others.

I think I will release soon.
